  "prompt": "How do I swim?",
  "response": "Here are basic steps to learn swimming:\n\n1. Get comfortable in water\n- Start in shallow water\n- Practice floating\n- Learn to control your breathing\n\n2. Basic techniques\n- Learn to tread water\n- Practice kicking while holding pool edge\n- Learn freestyle (front crawl) stroke\n- Keep your body horizontal\n- Kick from your hips\n- Rotate arms in alternating motion\n- Breathe to the side\n\n3. Safety tips\n- Always swim with supervision\n- Learn in a pool with a lifeguard\n- Wear flotation devices when learning\n- Start in shallow water\n- Learn proper breathing techniques\n\n4. Consider lessons\n- Take swimming classes\n- Learn from a professional instructor\n- Group or private lessons available\n\n5. Practice regularly\n- Build confidence gradually\n- Start in shallow water\n- Practice different strokes\n- Improve endurance and technique\n\nRemember, learning to swim takes time and patience. Don't get discouraged, and always prioritize safety.\n\nWould you like more detailed information about any of these steps?",
